snippet: Dustin Johnson didn't flinch when a challenge arrived out of nowhere Sunday, playing mistake-free over the final five holes to win the Mexico Championship in his debut as the No. 1 player in the world....

headline.main: Keselowski Steals Atlanta Win After Harvick Caught Speeding
headline.print_headline: Keselowski Steals Atlanta Win After Harvick Caught Speeding

lead_paragraph: Dustin Johnson didn't flinch when a challenge arrived out of nowhere Sunday, playing mistake-free over the final five holes to win the Mexico Championship in his debut as the No. 1 player in the world.
